<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Payment Success</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f6d365, #fda085);
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #f77f00;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin: 10px 0;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .credit {
            color: #388e3c;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.5em;
        }
        .cta {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .cta a {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #f77f00;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .cta a:hover {
            background-color: #d65a00;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You, <%= first_name %>!</h1>
        <p>Your payment was successful, and your wallet balance <span class="credit"><%=credit%>!</span>.</p>
        <p>We appreciate your support and hope you enjoy using our services.</p>
        <div class="cta">
            <a href="https://storylimo.com/billing">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,</p>
            <p><strong>StoryLimo Team</strong></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
